This repository is a fork of Freeciv.

Original project: https://github.com/freeciv/freeciv

This fork is licensed under the same GNU General Public License v2 as the
original project.

Modifications in this fork replace the centralized client-server networking
layer with decentralized peer-to-peer networking using Nostr (for
cryptographic game state verification) and Iroh (for direct P2P transport).
